flowchart LR
    SCHEMA[Schema Registry]

    SCHEMA --> COMPAT{backward compatible?}
    COMPAT -->|yes| MERGE[merge / publish new version]
    COMPAT -->|no| BREAK[breaking change policy]
    BREAK --> NEWVER[new major version namespace]
    NEWVER --> COEXIST[old + new coexist until sunset]
    COEXIST --> DEPRECATE[deprecate old]
    DEPRECATE --> SUNSET[sunset old after grace period]
    MERGE --> NOTIFY[notify consumers via changelog]
